      "bgmDelay": 2,
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "指挥官自己也许不觉得，不过……",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "无论是安静地欣赏我跳舞，还是放任我做想做的事情，还有和我一起吃甜点——",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "埃米尔露出十分甜蜜的微笑",
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "这些对我来说，都是最浪漫的事哟？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "甜言蜜语也好，惊喜也好，没有一颗真正为对方着想的心，就只是空洞的话语，和俗套的行为",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "而只有了解了一个人想要些什么，才能走进每个人的内心。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "我会喜欢指挥官，也是因为指挥官知道我想要什么，并把它给了我",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "能遇到指挥官实在是太好了呢~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "……总觉得被说了十分浪漫的话",
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "希望理解对方，让对方心动，想要对方能够了解自己心意的感情……",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "如果这都不能称为爱，那么还有什么东西配得上这个名号呢？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "……啊，忽然变得想要跳舞了呢~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
